Package: rfInterface
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Using UK Riverflow and Rainfall API
Date: 2018-12-17
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Adam Griffin <adagri@ceh.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Adam Griffin <adagri@ceh.ac.uk>
Description: rfInterface provides functions to easily access EA and NRFA river
    flow data and SEPA rainfall data, with utility functions to convert station
    identifiers and location grid references. Preview of data at 
    https://gateway-staging.ceh.ac.uk/hydrology-ukscape.
